title: I can't view my match history??

replies.body: There's been a few reports on this where some players can't view their history on the site.  I don't have any information or ETA's, but you can try clearing your [cache ](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies)or another browser to see if that works.  I hope that helps!
Same problem here but worse, i cannot view it with the webpage, in client or even websites like na.op.gg so i am pretty sure it is a issue on your end not ours.
If you're on Chrome, what happens if you try tapping: Ctrl + Shift + R?
Client and websites recovered on their own after several hours so it was definitely on your end server wise, ty for help though.

@Porocles, yeah there are some issues that people have seen. In a few under the bug reports board, a couple of us have identified that that the issue (likely) lies in the CDN cache somewhere, with a partial JS file (usually twig.js). Not sure how there is only a partial file, and why it only manifests for certain users, but it's a start for your web dev team.
